## Idle Detection
Algorithm:
1. Every 5s, take --robot-snapshot
2. Compare output_tail_lines for each agent to previous snapshot
3. If byte-identical (same count) for 3 consecutive snapshots (15s) → declare agent idle
4. After 30min absolute timeout → declare agent idle regardless

Action on idle: log to phase_events, show in dashboard as yellow indicator.
Do NOT auto-send prompts to idle agents — that's the human's decision via the dashboard.

```typescript
class IdleDetector {
  private history = new Map<string, number[]>();  // pane → last 3 tail_line counts

  check(snapshot: NtmSnapshot): Set<string> {
    const idle = new Set<string>();
    for (const session of snapshot.sessions) {
      for (const agent of session.agents) {
        const key = `${session.name}:${agent.pane}`;
        const hist = this.history.get(key) ?? [];
        hist.push(agent.output_tail_lines);
        if (hist.length > 3) hist.shift();
        this.history.set(key, hist);
        if (hist.length === 3 && hist.every(n => n === hist[0])) idle.add(key);
      }
    }
    return idle;
  }
}
```

